<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Shortlist Notification</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Congratulations, {{name}}!</h2>
  <p>We are pleased to inform you that you have been shortlisted for the following round:</p>
  <p><strong>Company:</strong> {{company}}</p>
  <p><strong>Role:</strong> {{role}}</p>
  <p><strong>Round:</strong> {{round}} ({{stage}})</p>
  <p><strong>Date & Time:</strong> {{roundDateTime}}</p>

  {{#if message}}
    <p><em>{{message}}</em></p>
  {{/if}}

  <p>Best of luck with your next steps!</p>

  <p>Regards,<br>The NIE Placement Cell</p>
</body>
</html>
